20diplomat%20Wang%20Yi%20discussed%20the%20border%20situation%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20reiterated%20the%20call%20for%20normalisation%20of%20bilateral%20relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20encounter%20took%20place%20in%20Johannesburg%20in%20South%20Africa%20where%20both%20attended%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20security%20advisors%20of%20the%20five%20members%20of%20the%20BRICS%20emerging%20countries%20bloc%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2024.%20Wang%20had%20previously%20met%20with%20Jaishankar%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20East%20Asia%20summit%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20on%20July%2014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20readout%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20Wang%20Yi%20had%20reiterated%20the%20usual%20talking%20points%20that%20the%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctruly%20implement%20the%20consensus%20on%20stabilizing%20bilateral%20relations%20into%20specific%20policies%2C%20and%20translate%20them%20into%20concerted%20actions%20by%20various%20departments%20and%20fields%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20asserted%20the%20countries%20should%20%E2%80%9Cfocus%20on%20consensus%20and%20cooperation%2C%20overcome%20interference%20and%20difficulties%2C%20and%20promote%20the%20return%20of%20bilateral%20relations%20to%20the%20track%20of%20healthy%20and%20stable%20development%20at%20an%20early%20date%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20press%20release%20also%20claimed%20that%20Wang%20Yi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20CPC%20Central%20Commission%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20reminded%20Doval%20that%20at%20end%20of%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9CPresident%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20reached%20an%20important%20consensus%20on%20stabilizing%20China-India%20relations%20in%20Bali%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20were%20in%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Bali%20in%20September%202022%20for%20the%20G-20%20summit.%20But%20as%20per%20information%20released%20by%20Indian%20official%20sources%2C%20there%20had%20been%20no%20meeting%20and%20they%20had%20only%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-modi-biden-xi-jinping%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexchanged%20courtesies%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20dinner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20had%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Ftopics_665678%2F2022%2Fcxesgjtytjhtg%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20issued%20any%20press%20notes%20during%20the%20G-20%20summit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20any%20meeting%20with%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20Doval%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Chinese%20readout%2C%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cis%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Chinese%20side%20to%20find%20a%20fundamental%20way%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20situation%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20mutual%20understanding%20and%20mutual%20respect%2C%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20situation%20and%20the%20long-term%2C%20promote%20the%20improvement%20and%20development%20of%20bilateral%20relations%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20make%20positive%20contributions%20to%20maintaining%20world%20peace%20and%20prosperity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20is%20a%20no%20Indian%20version%20of%20the%20talks%2C%20India%20has%20usually%20insisted%20that%20normalisation%20of%20the%20relations%20can%20only%20take%20place%20after%20all%20the%20friction%20points%20of%20the%20stand-off%20are%20resolved.%20China%20has%20insisted%20that%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20current%20stand-off%2C%20but%20are%20legacy%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20larger%20boundary%20dispute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20%E2%80%98Friends%20of%20BRICS%E2%80%99%20meeting%20on%20cybersecurity%2C%20Doval%20apparently%20highlighted%20the%20linkages%20between%20cyber%20criminals%20and%20terrorists%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20cyberspace%20for%20financing%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20radicalising%2C%20lone%20wolf%20attacks%2C%20recruitment%20and%20secured%20communications%2C%20as%20per%20official%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoval%20observed%20that%20the%20younger%20population%2C%20being%20tech-savvy%20and%20having%20impressionable%20minds%2C%20is%20especially%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20dissemination%20of%20extremist%20ideologies%20through%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690255107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25084633%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwang-yi-ajit-doval-india-china-brics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20encounter%20took%20place%20in%20Johannesburg%20in%20South%20Africa%20where%20both%20attended%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20security%20advisors%20of%20the%20five%20members%20of%20the%20BRICS%20emerging%20countries%20bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwang-yi-ajit-doval-india-china-brics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twitter%20Turning%20Into%20X%20Is%20Set%20To%20Kill%20Billions%20In%20Brand%20Value%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt's%20rare%20for%20corporate%20brands%20to%20become%20so%20intertwined%20with%20everyday%20conversation%20that%20they%20become%20verbs.%20It's%20rarer%20still%20for%20the%20owner%20of%20such%20a%20brand%20to%20announce%20plans%20to%20intentionally%20destroy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20quiet%20summer%20weekend%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20decreed%20that%20Twitter's%20product%20name%20would%20be%20changed%20to%20%26quot%3BX%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20is%20getting%20rid%20of%20the%20bird%20logo%20and%20all%20the%20associated%20words%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Btweet.%26quot%3B%20Musk's%20move%20wiped%20out%20anywhere%20between%20%244%20billion%20and%20%2420%20billion%20in%20value%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20and%20brand%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%2015-plus%20years%20to%20earn%20that%20much%20equity%20worldwide%2C%20so%20losing%20Twitter%20as%20a%20brand%20name%20is%20a%20significant%20financial%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Susi%2C%20director%20of%20brand%20communication%20at%20Siegel%20%26amp%3B%20Gale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20whose%20company%20has%20already%20declined%20significantly%20in%20value%20since%20he%20purchased%20it%20for%20%2444%20billion%20in%20October%2C%20announced%20the%20change%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20By%20Monday%20morning%20a%20new%20black%20%26quot%3BX%26quot%3B%20logo%2C%20designed%20by%20a%20fan%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20began%20to%20appear%20across%20the%20site.%20New%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Linda%20Yaccarino%20outlined%20the%20company's%20vision%20for%20X%20to%20become%20a%20site%20for%20audio%2C%20video%2C%20messaging%2C%20payments%20and%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20and%20brand%20agencies%20call%20the%20product's%20renaming%20a%20mistake.%20Twitter%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognizable%20social%20media%20brands%2C%20said%20Todd%20Irwin%2C%20founder%20of%20brand%20agency%20Fazer.%20Bird%20decals%20adorn%20small%20businesses%20and%20websites%20worldwide%2C%20alongside%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20logos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwitter's%20popularity%20has%20also%20made%20verbs%20like%20%26quot%3Btweet%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bretweet%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20modern%20culture%2C%20used%20regularly%20to%20explain%20how%20celebrities%2C%20politicians%20and%20others%20communicated%20with%20the%20public%2C%20said%20Joshua%20White%2C%20assistant%20professor%20of%20finance%20at%20Vanderbilt%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20will%20require%20the%20company%20to%20rebuild%20that%20cultural%20pull%20and%20linguistic%20consensus%20from%20scratch.%20But%20that%20may%20be%20part%20of%20the%20motivation%2C%20so%20users%20stop%20comparing%20Twitter%20post-takeover%20to%20what%20it%20was%20before.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20exceptionally%20rare%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20in%20life%20or%20in%20business%20%E2%80%94%20that%20you%20get%20a%20second%20chance%20to%20make%20another%20big%20impression%2C%26quot%3B%20Yaccarino%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20companies%20have%20renamed%20themselves%20in%20recent%20years.%20Google%20turned%20into%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20to%20allow%20different%20businesses%20within%20the%20company%20to%20grow%20without%20being%20tied%20to%20search.%20Facebook%20changed%20into%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%20in%20order%20to%20emphasize%20the%20company's%20commitment%20to%20the%20metaverse.%20But%20the%20product%20names%20remained%3B%20we%20still%20google%20things%20by%20going%20to%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20worth%20a%20lot.%20Twitter's%20brand%20value%20is%20estimated%20at%20about%20%244%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20brand%20valuation%20consulting%20firm%20Brand%20Finance.%20The%20firm%20values%20the%20Facebook%20brand%20at%20%2459%20billion%20and%20Instagram%20at%20%2447.4%20billion.%20Vanderbilt%20University%20estimates%20Twitter's%20brand%20value%20at%20%2415%20billion%20to%20%2420%20billion%2C%20which%20is%20comparable%20to%20Snapchat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrand%20valuation%20is%20difficult%20to%20determine%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20single%20approach%2C%20which%20is%20why%20estimates%20vary%2C%20said%20Dipanjan%20Chatterjee%2C%20an%20analyst%20with%20Forrester%20Research%20Inc.%20But%20several%20analysts%20and%20agencies%20agreed%20that%20the%20company's%20brand%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20significant%20hit%20since%20Musk's%20takeover.%20Brand%20Finance%20for%20example%2C%20estimates%20the%20Twitter%20brand%20lost%2032%25%20of%20its%20value%20since%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20perception%20of%20Twitter's%20brand%20has%20changed%2C%20advertisers%20have%20fled.%20Advertisers%20were%20concerned%20about%20Musk's%20courting%20of%20controversy%20and%20embrace%20of%20tweeters%20who%20broke%20content%20rules.%20Advertising%20revenue%20at%20Twitter%20is%20down%20more%20than%2050%25%20since%20October%2C%20Musk%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwitter's%20corporate%20brand%20is%20already%20heavily%20intertwined%20with%20Musk's%20personal%20brand%2C%20with%20or%20without%20the%20name%20X%2C%20and%20much%20of%20Twitter's%20established%20brand%20equity%20has%20already%20been%20lost%20among%20users%20and%20advertisers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jasmine%20Enberg%2C%20an%20analyst%20with%20Insider%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20irrational%20from%20a%20business%20and%20brand%20point%20of%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Allen%20Adamson%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20marketing%20and%20brand%20consulting%20group%20Metaforce.%20He%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bego%20decision%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Musk.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20unwinding%20of%20a%20business%20and%20brand%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22q4jpcj9k%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fq4jpcj9k_twitter-headquarters-in-san-francisco-bloomberg_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20partially%20removed%20sign%20at%20Twitter%20headquarters%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20risk%20to%20Musk's%20future%20goals.%20Building%20banking%20and%20payments%20into%20the%20app%20will%20require%20customer%20trust%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that's%20difficult%20to%20get%20with%20a%20brand-new%20product%20name.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20think%20that%20customers%20outside%20of%20Musk's%20sort%20of%20core%20fan%20base%20would%20really%20struggle%20to%20use%20Twitter%20to%20exchange%20their%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Vanderbilt's%20White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20working%20in%20Musk's%20favor%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Elon%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Irwin.%20%26quot%3BHis%20personal%20brand%20might%20be%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20Twitter%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690254480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fgv6b6frs_twitter-x-bloomberg_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwitter-turning-into-x-is-set-to-kill-billions-in-brand-value-4238537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20rare%20for%20corporate%20brands%20to%20become%20so%20intertwined%20with%20everyday%20conversation%20that%20they%20become%20verbs.%20It's%20rarer%20still%20for%20the%20owner%20of%20such%20a%20brand%20to%20announce%20plans%20to%20intentionally%20destroy%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwitter-turning-into-x-is-set-to-kill-billions-in-brand-value-4238537%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwitter-turning-into-x-is-set-to-kill-billions-in-brand-value-4238537%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwitter-turning-into-x-is-set-to-kill-billions-in-brand-value-4238537%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brazil's%20Ary%20Borges%20outdoes%20Pele%20with%20a%20World%20Cup%20hat-trick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690254416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstati