0its%20demand%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20speak%20in%20parliament%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue.%20On%20its%20part%2C%20the%20government%20is%20firm%20on%20its%20refusal%2C%20assuming%20that%20the%20opposition's%20demand%20is%20powered%20by%20electoral%20compulsions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20government%20will%20now%20insist%20on%20settling%20its%20legislative%20work%2C%20sources%20said.%20If%20a%20bill%20has%20to%20be%20passed%20amid%20uproar%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Union%20Home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20for%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%20But%20the%20government%20is%20clear%20that%20only%20the%20Home%20Minister%20will%20speak%20on%20the%20Manipur%20situation%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20government%20has%20already%20tried%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20through%20discussion.%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20spoken%20to%20top%20opposition%20leaders%20over%20phone.%20But%20with%20the%20opposition%20adamantly%20against%20budging%2C%20a%20flurry%20of%20meetings%20took%20place%20on%20the%20government%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20senior%20ministers%20have%20met%20PM%20Modi.%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20have%20met%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20the%20current%20approach%20has%20been%20decided%20on%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20drawn%20up%20a%20heavy%20legislative%20schedule%20with%2031%20bills%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session.%20Among%20them%20is%20a%20bill%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20Ordinance%20that%20gives%20Centre%20the%20power%20to%20control%20bureaucrats%20posted%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20also%20determined%20to%20not%20allow%20any%20legislative%20schedule%20before%20the%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%20And%20even%20before%20that%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%20in%20parliament%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20Manipur%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20gravest%20crisis%20our%20country%20has%20faced%20in%20a%20long%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20horrendous%20loss%20of%20lives...%20there%20were%20rapes%20and%20violence%20and%20displacement.%20And%20now%20it%20is%20spreading.%20In%20Mizoram%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20backlash%20and%20Meities%20are%20fleeing%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%2C%20declaring%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20more%20important%20subject%20that%20needs%20PM%20Modi's%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20northeastern%20state%20has%20witnessed%20terrible%20violence%20before.%20But%20No%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20visited%20the%20state%20when%20violence%20took%20place%20in%201993%20and%201997.%20it%20was%20not%20discussed%20in%20parliament%20and%20only%20on%20one%20instance%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20had%20given%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20however%2C%20has%20been%20a%20rethink%20on%20how%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue.%20Sources%20said%20the%20government%20will%20limit%20its%20reply%20in%20parliament%20only%20to%20Manipur%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20mention%20of%20violence%20in%20Opposition-ruled%20states%20-which%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20cited%20over%20the%20last%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20under%20control%20in%20Manipur%20now%20and%20no%20one%20died%20in%20violence%20in%20last%2015%20days%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690250460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F2bsg4db8_parliament-house-pti_625x300_15_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-manipur-impasse-be-resolve