surfaced%20online%20showing%20two%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20accused%20was%20arrested%20from%20Thoubal%20district%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20the%20two%20women%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20all%20quarters.%20A%20tribal%20organisation%20in%20Manipur%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20two%20women%20were%20gang-raped%20in%20a%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders'%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20alleges%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20on%20May%204%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%2035%20kilometers%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20of%20Imphal.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20maintain%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20in%20a%20different%20district%2C%20despite%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20being%20filed%20in%20Kangpokpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20arrest%20was%20made%20by%20the%20police%20on%20Thursday%2C%20July%2020%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%2026-second%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20surfaced%20online.%20Three%20more%20arrests%20were%20made%20later%20that%20day.%20A%20fifth%20accused%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20Saturday%20is%20a%2019-year-old%20while%20the%20sixth%20person%20taken%20into%20custody%20is%20a%20minor%2C%20the%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20horrific%20incident%20took%20place%20a%20day%20after%20violence%20erupted%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20following%20the%20Meitei's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20status.%20The%20violence%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20has%20so%20far%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20120%20people%20and%20displaced%20thousands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20has%20rocked%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20parliament.%20A%20group%20of%20opposition%20MPs%20are%20staging%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20in%20front%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20statue%20at%20Parliament%20House%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20government%20allow%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20free%20and%20unfettered%20debate%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20without%20any%20time%20constraints%2C%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20demand%20is%20that%20the%20PM%20should%20come%20to%20the%20house%20and%20make%20a%20statement.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20discuss%20that%20statement.%20You%20are%20speaking%20outside%20but%20not%20inside%2C%20this%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20parliament.%20It%20is%20a%20serious%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20opposition's%20allegations%2C%20the%20BJP%20retorted%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20opposition%20was%20shirking%20a%20debate%20on%20Manipur%20and%20criticised%20their%20%26quot%3Bdeafening%20silence%26quot%3B%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690248600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F1ovnf21o_manipur-crime-ndtv-650_650x400_20_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-video-manipur-violence-7th-accused-arrested-over-manipur-video-of-women-paraded-naked-4238461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seventh%20accused%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20horrific%20video%20that%20surfaced%20online%20showing%20two%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-video-manipur-violence-7th-accused-arrested-over-manipur-video-of-women-paraded-naked-4238461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-video-