%20the%20confrontation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MANOSH%20DAS%20AND%20PRABIN%20KALITA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmob-attacks-meghalaya-cm-conrad-sangmas-meet-with-garo-outfit%2Farticleshow%2F102089564.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Hunter%20Biden's%20gallery%20sold%20his%20art%20to%20a%20Democratic%20donor%20'friend'%20who%20Joe%20Biden%20named%20to%20a%20prestigious%20commission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Joe%20Biden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64beaf0abea34400196014e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHunter%20Biden%20sold%20artwork%20to%20Elizabeth%20Hirsh%20Naftali%2C%20a%20Democratic%20donor%20who%20was%20appointed%20to%20a%20prestigious%20federal%20commission%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people%20directly%20familiar%20with%20Hunter%20Biden's%20account.%20The%20transaction%20raises%20questions%20about%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20pledge%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20wall%26quot%3B%20separating%20his%20administration%20from%20his%20family%20members'%20business%20deals.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FAP%3B%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsider%20has%20learned%20the%20identities%20of%20two%20Hunter%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bfriends%26quot%3B%20who%20were%20also%20buyers%20of%20his%20art%3A%20Elizabeth%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20and%20Kevin%20Morris.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternal%20gallery%20documents%20reveal%20that%20sales%20of%20Hunter%20Biden's%20art%20brought%20in%20%241.3%20million.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20buyer%2C%20identity%20unknown%2C%20spent%20%24875%2C000%20on%2011%20Hunter%20Biden%20artworks.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20pledged%20that%20there%20would%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20wall%26quot%3B%20between%20his%20official%20duties%20and%20his%20family's%20private%20business%20interests.%20The%20Biden%20White%20House%20repeatedly%20made%20reference%20to%20that%20wall%20when%20responding%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20fledgling%20art%20career%20of%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20the%20president's%20son.%20In%202021%2C%20when%20a%20New%20York%20art%20gallery%20debuted%20Hunter%20Biden's%20paintings%20with%20asking%20prices%20as%20high%20as%20%24500%2C000%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20that%20Hunter%20Biden's%20team%20had%20a%20process%20for%20carefully%20vetting%20buyers%2C%20and%20that%20their%20identities%20were%20known%20only%20to%20the%20gallery%2C%20and%20not%20to%20Hunter%20Biden%20himself.%20The%20messaging%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20Hunter%20Biden's%20art%20patrons%20came%20from%20a%20rarified%20universe%20of%20collectors%20who%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20hurly%20burly%20of%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20those%20things%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20Hunter%20Biden%20did%20in%20fact%20learn%20the%20identity%20of%20two%20buyers%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people%20directly%20familiar%20with%20Hunter%20Biden's%20own%20account%20of%20his%20art%20career.%20And%20one%20of%20those%20buyers%20is%20indeed%20someone%20who%20got%20a%20favor%20from%20the%20Biden%20White%20House.%20The%20timing%20of%20their%20purchase%2C%20however%2C%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20buyer%2C%20Insider%20can%20reveal%2C%20is%20Elizabeth%20Hirsh%20Naftali%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20real%20estate%20investor%20and%20philanthropist.%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20is%20influential%20in%20California%20Democratic%20circles%20and%20is%20a%20significant%20Democratic%20donor%20who%20has%20given%20%2413%2C414%20to%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20and%20%2429%2C700%20to%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Campaign%20Committee%20this%20year.%20In%202022%2C%20she%20hosted%20a%20fundraiser%20headlined%20by%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20also%20obtained%20internal%20documents%20from%20Hunter%20Biden's%20gallery%20showing%20that%20a%20single%20buyer%20purchased%20%24875%2C000%20of%20his%20art.%20The%20documents%20do%20not%20indicate%20the%20buyer's%20identity%2C%20which%20is%20also%20unknown%20to%20Insider%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20eight%20months%20after%20Hunter%20Biden's%20first%20art%20opening%2C%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2022%2F07%2F01%2Fpresident-biden-announces-key-appointments-to-boards-and-commissions-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20Hirsh%20Naftali's%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Commission%20for%20the%20Preservation%20of%20America's%20Heritage%20Abroad.%20It%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Hirsh's%20purchase%20of%20Hunter%20Biden's%20artwork%20occurred%20before%20or%20after%20that%20appointment.%20Membership%20on%20the%20commission%20is%20an%20unpaid%20position%20that%20is%20often%20filled%20by%20campaign%20donors%2C%20family%20members%2C%20and%20political%20allies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20crowd%20that%20often%20winds%20up%20with%20US%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F12%2F15%2Fopinion%2Fambassadors-donors-biden.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eambassadorial%20appointments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hirsh%20Naftali's%20fundraising%20activities%20mark%20her%20as%20the%20kind%20of%20well-connected%20donor%20who%20often%20wins%20such%20appointments%2C%20regardless%20of%20any%20relationship%20they%20might%20have%20with%20the%20president's%20family.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20address%20the%20possibility%20that%20Hunter%20Biden%20might%20have%20voiced%20his%20support%20for%20her%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20did%20that%20happen%20or%20not%3F%20Did%20Hunter%20Biden%20weigh%20in%20with%20his%20father%20about%20the%20appointment%20of%20Hirsh%20Naftali%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20did%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20buy%20Hunter%20Biden's%20art%20before%20or%20after%20she%20was%20appointed%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20asked%20these%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20White%20House%20nor%20Hunter%20Biden's%20counsel%20could%20offer%20an%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20should%20that%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHirsh%20Naftali%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20administration%20official%20told%20Insider%20that%20her%20appointment%20had%20been%20recommended%20to%20Biden%20by%20former%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi.%20They%20said%20there%20was%20no%20connection%20between%20her%20art%20purchases%20and%20her%20appointment.%20They%20said%20that%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20was%20deeply%20involved%20with%20Jewish%20causes%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Israel%20%E2%80%94%20valuable%20background%20for%20a%20commission%20that%20works%20to%20preserve%20many%20historic%20Jewish%20sites%20across%20Europe.%20They%20noted%20her%20service%20on%20a%20policy%20board%20at%20the%20RAND%20Corporation%2C%20a%20prominent%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20not%20offer%20a%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHunter%20Biden%20is%20a%20private%20citizen%20who%20is%20entitled%20to%20have%20his%20own%20career%20as%20an%20artist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ian%20Sams%2C%20a%20White%20House%20spokesperson.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20his%20art%20sales%2C%20and%20any%20buyers%20of%20his%20art%20are%20not%20disclosed%20to%20the%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBruce%20Weinstein%2C%20a%20professional%20ethicist%20and%20ethics%20trainer%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20Hirsh%20Naftali's%20purchase%20was%20significant.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20was%20done%20after%20her%20appointment%2C%20and%20she%20likes%20the%20painting%2C%20it's%20less%20of%20an%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20of%20an%20issue%20if%20she's%20deciding%20to%20buy%20it%20beforehand.%20Then%20it%20might%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20regardless%20of%20the%20timing%2C%20Weinstein%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20really%20wanted%20to%20choose%20the%20most%20ethically%20appropriate%20course%20of%20action%2C%20that%20would%20not%20involve%20any%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20real%20or%20perceived%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20buy%20the%20painting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20for%20the%20Preservation%20of%20America's%20Heritage%20Abroad%20is%20a%20public%20agency%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heritageabroad.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUnited-States-Code-Title-54-Chapter-3123_Law-establishing-Commission.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarged%20with%20preserving%3C%2Fa%3E%20European%20historical%20sites.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Hunter%20Biden%20has%20privately%20suggested%20that%20he%20could%20arrange%20to%20have%20friends%20seated%20on%20the%20commission.%20Eric%20Schwerin%2C%20Hunter%20Biden's%20longtime%20business%20associate%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fobamawhitehouse.archives.gov%2Fthe-press-office%2F2015%2F03%2F10%2Fpresident-obama-announces-more-key-administration-posts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappointed%20to%20the%20same%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20in%202015.%20An%20email%20apparently%20from%20Hunter%20Biden's%20abandoned%20laptop%20written%20that%20year%20suggests%20that%20he%20had%20sway%20over%20Schwerin's%20appointment.%20%26quot%3BEric%20asked%20me%20for%20one%20of%20these%20the%20day%20after%20the%20election%20in%202008%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20wrote%20to%20a%20cousin%2C%20who%20had%20written%20inquiring%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20similar%20appointment%20for%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Hunter%20Biden%20nor%20Schwerin%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20email's%20contents.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20Abbe%20Lowell%2C%20Hunter%20Biden's%20counsel%2C%20said%20that%20Hunter%20Biden%20learned%20the%20identities%20of%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20and%20a%20second%20buyer%20after%20they%20had%20purchased%20his%20art%20through%20his%20gallery%2C%20because%20they%20were%20his%20friends.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gallery%20sets%20the%20pricing%20and%20handles%20all%20sales%20based%20on%20the%20highest%20ethical%20standards%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20does%20not%20disclose%20the%20names%20of%20any%20purchasers%20to%20Mr.%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20Lowell%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNames%20of%20buyers%20are%20strictly%20confidential%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Georges%20Berg%C3%A8s%2C%20Hunter%20Biden's%20gallerist%2C%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BAny%20attempt%20to%20get%20them%20is%20illegal%20and%20will%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20proper%20authorities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hunter%20Biden%20deplanes%20from%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%20Syracuse%2C%20New%20York%2C%20on%20February%204%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649361641465b60019988a81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHunter%20Biden%20deplanes%20from%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%20Syracuse%2C%20New%20York%2C%20on%20February%204%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Frantz%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EDocument%20points%20to%20%24875%2C000%20mystery%20buyer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20Georges%20Berg%C3%A8s%20Gallery%20documents%20obtained%20by%20Insider%2C%20a%20selection%20of%20which%20are%20published%20below%2C%20show%20that%20a%20single%20buyer%20purchased%2011%20Hunter%20Biden%20artworks%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%24875%2C000.%20A%20gallery%20contract%20with%20Hunter%20Biden's%20handwritten%20edits%20show%20him%20excluding%20the%20sales%20of%20NFTs%20from%20the%20gallery's%2040%20percent%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23885595-hunter-biden-georges-berges-gallery-documents-two-pages%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26responsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Hunter%20Biden%20%2F%20Georges%20Berges%20Gallery%20documents%3B%20two%20pages%20(Hosted%20by%20DocumentCloud)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22903%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20identity%20of%20the%20%24875%2C000%20buyer%20is%20unclear.%20That%20one%20buyer%20represents%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20%241%2C379%2C000%20in%20receipts%20that%20Hunter%20Biden's%20gallery%20received%20for%20his%20work%2C%20the%20documents%20show%2C%20with%20the%20gallery%20receiving%20a%2040%20to%2045%20percent%20commission.%20The%20%24875%2C000%20art%20buyer%20resides%20outside%20New%20York%20and%20purchased%20some%20of%20Hunter%20Biden's%20largest%20format%20works%2C%20including%20a%2012-foot-long%20red-white-and-blue%20piece%20painted%20on%20sheet%20metal%20and%20entitled%20%26quot%3BPandemonium.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20art%20buyer%20known%20to%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20according%20to%20the%20three%20people%20directly%20familiar%20with%20Hunter%20Biden's%20own%20account%2C%20is%20Kevin%20Morris%2C%20a%20wealthy%20Los%20Angeles%20attorney%20who%20has%20become%20Biden's%20confidant%20and%20financial%20backer.%20Morris's%20ownership%20of%20Biden's%20art%20was%20previously%20reported%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20although%20a%20person%20close%20to%20Morris%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F05%2F10%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fhunter-biden-kevin-morris-lawyer.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20suggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Times%20that%20the%20art%20may%20have%20been%20a%20gift%2C%20not%20a%20purchase.%20In%20fact%2C%20according%20to%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20Hunter%20Biden's%20account%2C%20Morris%20purchased%20the%20art%20through%20Biden's%20gallery.%20In%20addition%20to%20collecting%20his%20work%2C%20Morris%20has%20reportedly%20lent%20Hunter%20Biden%20upwards%20of%20%242%20million%2C%20helping%20him%20pay%20off%20back%20taxes%20and%20avoid%20felony%20penalties%20under%20a%20June%20settlement%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20Instead%2C%20Hunter%20Biden%20pled%20guilty%20to%20two%20misdemeanor%20tax%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorris%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20asking%20prices%20for%20Hunter%20Biden's%20artwork%20may%20appear%20staggering%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20unreasonable%20given%20the%20vagaries%20of%20the%20art%20market%20according%20to%20Charlie%20Horne%2C%20president%20of%20Gurr%20Johns%2C%20an%20art%20advisory%20and%20appraisal%20company.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20ton%20of%20terrible%20artists%20who%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20told%20me%20that%20each%20of%20his%20paintings%20was%20a%20million%20dollars%2C%20and%20that%20he'd%20never%20had%20a%20museum%20show%2C%20that%20would%20be%20one%20thing.%20But%20anything%20under%20%24100%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20at%20those%20prices%2C%20it's%20very%20subjective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKedric%20Payne%2C%20general%20counsel%20at%20the%20Campaign%20Legal%20Center%2C%20said%20that%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20Hirsh%20Naftali%20appointment%20was%20an%20ethics%20violation%20depended%20on%20both%20the%20timing%20of%20her%20purchase%20and%20whether%20the%20art%20was%20purchased%20at%20fair%20market%20prices%2C%20or%20for%20substantially%20more%2C%20in%20which%20case%20it%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegally%2C%20you%20might%20not%20have%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20with%20the%20appearance%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20to%20try%20and%20explain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMattathias%20Schwartz%20is%20Insider's%20chief%20national%20security%20correspondent.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20by%20email%20at%20schwartz79%40protonmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhunter-biden-joe-artwork-berges-gallery-elizabeth-hirsh-naftali-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690234566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64be8502ed4f46001961d5d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhunter-biden-joe-artwork-berges-gallery-elizabeth-hirsh-naftali-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20ethics%20expert%20said%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Hunter%20Biden%20art%20buyer%20to%20a%20US%20commission%20could%20raise%20concerns%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bquid%20pro%20quo.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mschwartz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mattathias%20Schwartz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A494%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhunter-biden-joe-artwork-berges-gallery-elizabeth-hirsh-naftali-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Greta%20Thunberg%20carried%20away%20by%20police%20hours%20after%20fine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690234398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F569A%2Fproduction%2F_130507122_p0g2q7g9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66295035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20climate%20activist%20was%20removed%20from%20a%20protest%20shortly%20after%20being%20fined%20over%20a%20previous%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww