electronic%20payments%2C%20making%20ATMs%20ripe%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20about%2030%20million%20euros%20were%20stolen%20via%20ATM%20bombings%2C%20up%2053%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20preference%20for%20physical%20currency%20may%20be%20costing%20the%20country%20dearly%2C%20as%20Europe's%20largest%20economy%20has%20seen%20an%20explosion%20in%20crime%20that%20features%20ATM%20bombings%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F5a03b08d-dc7e-4115-b6aa-139e1ec39b99%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Germans%20have%20long%20favored%20buying%20things%20with%20cash%20instead%20of%20cards%20or%20other%20form%20of%20electronic%20payments%2C%20organized%20criminals%20have%20exploited%20this%20habit%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20496%20ATMs%20were%20blown%20up%20as%20part%20of%20cash-grab%20heists%2C%20a%2027%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20the%20Federal%20Criminal%20Police%20Office%20told%20the%20FT.%20On%20average%2C%20such%20raids%20could%20yield%20100%2C000%20euros%2C%20equivalent%20to%20%24110%2C686.5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20translated%20to%2030%20million%20euros%20that%20were%20stolen%20via%20ATM%20bombings%20last%20year%2C%20up%2053%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20Germans%20prefer%20physical%20banknotes%20over%20cards%20or%20digital%20tender%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20country%20has%20over%2055%2C000%20ATMs%20filled%20with%20high-denomination%20euros.%20For%20the%20culprits%2C%20it's%20a%20unique%20target%2C%20as%20other%20European%20states%20undergo%20a%20decline%20of%20cash%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20no%20one%20has%20been%20seriously%20injured%20or%20killed%20during%20these%20bombings%2C%20they%20are%20not%20risk-free%20ventures%2C%20FT%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20the%20culprits%20themselves%20get%20hurt%20in%20the%20explosion%2C%20while%20the%20car%20ride%20away%20is%20characterized%20by%20high%20speeds%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20fiery%20collisions.%20It's%20a%20danger%20made%20worse%20by%20fuel%20canisters%20the%20robbers%20carry%20for%20refueling%2C%20which%20also%20discourages%20officers%20from%20shooting%20at%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20response%20has%20been%20largely%20fragmented.%20Efforts%20to%20implement%20effective%20ATM%20and%20law%20enforcement%20standards%20are%20diluted%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20Germany%20has%20over%201%2C500%20lenders%2C%20while%20each%20province%20leads%20its%20own%20policing%20task%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20Netherlands%20have%20implemented%20protection%20systems%20that%20glue%20cash%20together%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20raid%2C%20this%20hasn't%20been%20carried%20out%20in%20Germany%20over%20health%20and%20safety%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20attempts%20to%20fortify%20ATMs%20against%20earlier%20types%20of%20detonations%20were%20thwarted%20when%20the%20criminals%20switched%20to%20different%20explosives%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20success%20has%20occurred%2C%20with%20police%20groups%20in%20one%20province%20learning%20to%20analyze%20potential%20escape%20routes%20as%20a%20way%20to%20prepare.%20And%20prosecutors%20of%20those%20captured%20are%20also%20starting%20to%20add%20attempted%20murder%20charges%20as%20the%20explosions%20put%20nearby%20residents%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerman-atm-bombing-gang-crime-wave-cash-preference-euro-banks-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690228770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bed5a1ed4f460019624969%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.co