adelphia.%20Traffic%20was%20severely%20affected%20due%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20this%20primary%20north-to-south%20highway%20for%20East%20Coast%20travel.%3Cp%3EMark%20Makela%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20I-95%20bridge%20in%20Philadelphia%20brought%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20busiest%20thoroughfares%20to%20a%20standstill.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20city's%20speedy%20reconstruction%20plan%20brought%20residents%20together%20in%20a%20rare%20show%20of%20engagement%20with%20public%20works.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECity%20transportation%20officials%20said%20completing%20a%20months-long%20project%20in%2012%20days%20was%20expensive%2C%20but%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvancing-cities%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3BAdvancing%20Cities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20highlighting%20urban%20centers%20across%20the%20US%20that%20are%20committed%20to%20improving%20life%20for%20their%20residents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20as%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20of%20Pennsylvania%20spoke%20to%20the%20press%20about%20the%20partial%20collapse%20of%20Interstate%2095%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20the%20faint%20sound%20of%20demolition%20work%20could%20be%20heard%20in%20the%20background.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%2010%20hours%20before%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpacast.com%2Fm%3Fp%3D23248%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShapiro%20spoke%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tanker%20truck%20carrying%208%2C500%20gallons%20of%20gasoline%20caught%20fire%20under%20an%20I-95%20ramp%2C%20causing%20part%20of%20the%20roadway%20to%20collapse%20and%20heavily%20damaging%20the%20southbound%20lanes%20of%20the%20highway.%20I-95%20was%20immediately%20closed%20in%20both%20directions%2C%20badly%20snarling%20traffic%20for%20the%20highway's%20160%2C000%20daily%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20disaster%2C%20Shapiro%20said%20it%20would%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20of%20months%26quot%3B%20before%20I-95%20was%20repaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBridge%20failures%20have%20become%20more%20common%2C%20with%201%20in%205%20miles%20of%20US%20highways%20and%20major%20roads%20in%20poor%20condition%2C%20according%20to%20the%20federal%20government's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2021%2F11%2F06%2Ffact-sheet-the-bipartisan-infrastructure-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfrastructure%20Investment%20and%20Jobs%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20law%2C%20passed%20in%202021%2C%20authorized%20%24110%20billion%20to%20help%20repair%20roads%20and%20bridges%2C%20which%20historically%20take%20months%20or%20years%20to%20repair.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20similar%20bridge%20collapse%20in%202017%20in%20Atlanta%20on%20Interstate%2085%20took%2043%20days%20to%20reopen%2C%20and%20it%20took%2013%20months%20to%20fix%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%20I-35W%20Mississippi%20River%20bridge%20in%20Minnesota%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20I-95%20reopened%20just%2012%20days%20later%2C%20restoring%20order%20on%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20thoroughfares%20in%20the%20area.%20How%20did%20the%20city%20do%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pennsylvania%20Governor%20Josh%20Shapiro%20speaking%20at%20a%20press%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b97bc44182d800196a48dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGovernor%20Josh%20Shapiro%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Department%20of%20Transportation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EQuick%20action%20from%20PennDOT%20officials%20and%20local%20contractors%20jump-started%20a%20speedy%20recovery%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20morning%20of%20June%2011%2C%20Lou%20Belmonte%2C%20a%20district%20executive%20for%20Pennsylvania's%20Department%20of%20Transportation%2C%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20a%20Philadelphia%20County%20maintenance%20manager%20about%20the%20collapse%20and%20quickly%20went%20into%20problem-solving%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelmonte%20told%20Insider%20his%20first%20thought%20was%20to%20use%20the%20southbound%20lanes%20to%20switch%20traffic%20and%20keep%20it%20going.%20However%2C%20he%20realized%20the%20southbound%20lanes%20weren't%20structurally%20sound%2C%20and%20by%20the%20time%20Shapiro%20was%20in%20the%20city%20hours%20later%2C%20demolition%20for%20the%20highway%20was%20already%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20another%20section%20of%20I-95%20was%20under%20active%20construction%2C%20so%20contractors%20and%20machinery%20were%20nearby.%20That%20quick%20work%2C%20Belmonte%20said%2C%20was%20one%20of%20many%20key%20decisions%20that%20got%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penndot.pa.gov%2FRegionalOffices%2Fdistrict-6%2FPages%2FAlertDetails.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereconstruction%20project%20moving%3C%2Fa%3E%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhiladelphians%20like%20their%20I-95%2C%26quot%3B%20Belmonte%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%20congestion%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fgraphics%2F2023%2F06%2F21%2Fi-95-traffic-detours-bridge-collapse%2F70336826007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimmediately%20spiked%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20roadways%20near%20the%20I-95%20collapse%20as%20emergency%20crews%20rushed%20to%20set%20up%20detours.%20For%20local%20officials%2C%20the%20pressure%20was%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aftermath%20of%20the%20collapse%20of%20I-95%20highway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64872e1405024f001902a609%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAftermath%20of%20the%20collapse%20of%20I-95%20highway%3Cp%3EBilly%20Kyle%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EStrong%20policy%20guardrails%20empowered%20the%20city%20to%20stick%20with%20local%20experts%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20quickly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20decision%20was%20the%20city's%20use%20of%20emergency%20rules%20allowing%20PennDOT%20to%20avoid%20a%20bidding%20process%20on%20the%20project%2C%20which%20was%20immediately%20handed%20to%20the%20Philadelphia%20construction%20firm%20Buckley%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20It%20had%20experience%20helping%20the%20nation's%20sixth-largest%20city%20with%20disaster-related%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20such%20as%C2%A0%20flooding%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhyy.org%2Farticles%2Fvine-street-expressway-fully-reopens-both-directions-after-historic-flooding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVine%20Street%20Expressway%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2015%2C%20Buckley%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20completed%20demolition%20after%20just%20four%20days%2C%20well%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%20Critically%2C%20it%20also%20had%20experience%20working%20with%20AeroAggregates%2C%20a%20lightweight%20backfill%20material%20made%20of%20recycled%20glass%20that%20was%20used%20to%20temporarily%20fix%20I-95.%20In%20construction%2C%20backfilling%20is%20the%20reuse%20of%20soil%20that's%20removed%20during%20excavation%20to%20strengthen%20a%20structure.%20Using%20lightweight%20fill%20saved%20Philadelphia%20weeks%20in%20getting%20I-95%20reopened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20it%20will%20work%20to%20rebuild%20beams%20under%20the%20highway%2C%20which%20can%20take%20eight%20to%2010%20weeks%20to%20fabricate.%20The%20permanent%20fix%20for%20the%20project%2C%20which%20will%20ensure%20six%20lanes%20of%20traffic%20are%20flowing%20at%20all%20times%2C%20won't%20be%20complete%20until%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhiladelphia%20has%20used%20AeroAggregates%20on%20only%20about%20half%20a%20dozen%20projects%2C%20as%20the%20specialty%20material%20is%20expensive%20and%20costs%20more%20than%20bringing%20in%20heftier%20dirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Construction%20crew%20and%20machinery%20converge%20of%20the%20damaged%20section%20of%20I-95%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b97c33245f83001904f8a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20I-95%20bridge%20reconstruction%20started%20quickly%20with%20aid%20of%20construction%20crew%20and%20machinery%20which%20was%20already%20near%20the%20scene.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Department%20of%20Transportation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EOther%20businesses%20shared%20resources%20as%20new%20delays%20hampered%20the%20reconstruction%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20project%20wrapped%20up%2C%20forecasts%20for%20rain%20led%20to%20a%20new%20threat%20that%20could%20hinder%20highway%20paint%20striping.%20The%20Pocono%20Raceway%20in%20Pennsylvania%20sent%20the%20city%20one%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autoweek.com%2Fracing%2Fnascar%2Fa44315047%2Fhow-nascar-jet-dryer-helped-open-i-95-in-philadelphia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASCAR%20jet%20dryers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20the%20roadway%20dry%20for%20one%20of%20the%20final%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20bridge%2C%20experts%20at%20the%20traffic-management%20company%20Inrix%20found%20that%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20%26quot%3Bhot%20spots%26quot%3B%20along%20some%20detour%20routes%20throughout%20the%20city%20showed%20that%20traffic%20speeds%20declined%20during%20rush%20hours%20as%20the%20reconstruction%20took%20place.%20Experts%20say%20that%20the%20end%20of%20the%20school%20year%2C%20slower%20traffic%20patterns%20due%20to%20city%20residents%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20the%20Jersey%20Shore%2C%20and%20work-from-home%20flexibility%20all%20led%20to%20fewer%20traffic%20problems%20than%20feared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20did%20a%20pretty%20good%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Bob%20Pishue%2C%20a%20transportation%20analyst%20at%20Inrix%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20did%20move%20it%20in%20pretty%20record%20time%2C%20and%20improving%20it%20would%20be%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20Ahramjian%2C%20an%20associate%20planner%20at%20the%20engineering%20consultant%20Kittelson%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%2C%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20has%20been%20a%20really%20great%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20government%20has%20the%20tools%20that%20it%20needs%2C%20it%20really%20is%20able%20to%20operate%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhramjian%2C%20who%20has%20done%20design%20work%20on%20walls%20and%20underpasses%20on%20I-95%2C%20said%20part%20of%20why%20traffic%20was%20relatively%20well%20controlled%20in%20the%20region%20was%20the%20availability%20of%20many%20alternative%20routes%2C%20including%20Philadelphia's%20Roosevelt%20Boulevard%20and%20I-295%20just%20across%20the%20Delaware%20River%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20a%20well-connected%20roadway%20network%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20places%20that%20those%20cars%20can%20go%20and%20different%20choices%20they%20can%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahramjian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Firefighter%20sprays%20water%20on%20the%20debris%20surrounding%20the%20I-95%20bridge%20in%20Philadelphia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b97d5b245f83001904fc02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Department%20of%20Transportation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20city's%20impressive%20response%20time%20leaves%20residents%20wondering%3A%20Why%20isn't%20everything%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20residents%20were%20impressed%20with%20the%20speediness%20of%20the%20I-95%20fix%2C%20some%20couldn't%20help%20but%20wonder%3A%20Why%20can't%20the%20city%20speed%20up%20other%20infrastructure%20projects%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20we%20just%20ask%20why%20the%20roads%20are%20not%20done%20if%20you%20guys%20got%20that%20little%20stretch%20done%20so%20fast%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20Stephanie%20Bartash%2C%20who%20resides%20in%20Ambler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20regularly%20uses%20I-95%20to%20get%20to%20her%20children%20who%20live%20north%20of%20the%20city.%20Bartash%20said%20her%20travel%20time%20to%20Bucks%20County%20doubled%20to%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20during%20the%20I-95%20bridge%20reconstruction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJo%20Bradley%2C%20who%20travels%20across%20Philadelphia%20for%20work%2C%20said%20she%20built%20in%20an%20extra%2020%20to%2025%20minutes%20to%20travel%20in%20the%20affected%20region%20near%20I-95.%20During%20the%20reconstruction%2C%20Bradley%20opted%20to%20take%20local%20roads%20in%20the%20city%20as%20an%20alternative%20commute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20the%20repair%20they've%20done%20as%20a%20Band-Aid%2C%20not%20a%20permanent%20repair%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20emergency%20repair.%20It%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20permanent%20repair%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20survive%20with%20for%20the%20next%2020-some%20odd%20years.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOfficials%20say%20cost%20is%20a%20barrier%20to%20a%20repeat%20performance%2C%20but%20residents%20give%20kudos%20for%20transparency%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speed%20of%20the%20I-95%20fix%2C%20however%2C%20was%20something%20to%20be%20celebrated.%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20after%2C%20I%20was%20very%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20they%20had%20it%20immediately%20organized%20because%20that%20is%20not%20an%20experience%20we%20have%20been%20having%20in%20Philadelphia%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartash%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nice%20for%20them%20to%20have%20a%20win.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20local%20residents%20praised%20the%20transparency%20of%20the%20project.%20PennDOT%20set%20up%20a%20livestream%20of%20the%20project%20so%20residents%20could%20watch%20the%20reconstruction%20anytime.%20The%20footage%20was%20aired%20locally%20at%20bars%20and%20even%20on%20the%20Philadelphia%20Phillies'%20baseball%20scoreboard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelmonte%20said%20he%20understood%20the%20desire%20to%20have%20other%20infrastructure%20projects%20completed%20faster%20but%20that%20having%20staff%20and%20contractors%20work%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20like%20the%20city%20did%20for%20the%20I-95%20fix%2C%20wasn't%20feasible.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20too%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20proud%20of%20what%20occurred%20after%20the%20tragedy.%20Someone%20lost%20their%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Belmonte%20said.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20circumstances%2C%20if%20someone%20said%20we%20could%20open%20in%2012%20days%2C%20every%20one%20of%20us%20would%20have%20taken%20that%20in%20the%20beginning.%20And%20I'd%20take%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphiladelphia-turns-heads-speedy-i-95-bridge-reconstruction%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690225478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b7eb1476558a00189d894e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphiladelphia-turns-heads-speedy-i-95-bridge-reconstruction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Philadelphia%20transportation%20officials%20share%20how%20they%20compl