vernment%20has%20not%20changed%20this%20stance%20since.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20despite%20all%20cheetahs%20dying%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%2C%20authorities%20are%20hurriedly%20subjecting%20all%20cheetahs%20to%20health%20checks.%20Free-ranging%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20which%20authorities%20had%20released%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20being%20captured%20and%20brought%20back%20into%20enclosures%20for%20health%20checks.%20Free-ranging%20female%20cheetah%20Gamini%20was%20brought%20to%20an%20enclosure%20in%20the%20Park%20and%20subjected%20to%20a%20health%20examination%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Forest%20Department%20announced%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fminforestmp%2Fstatus%2F1682652784800276480%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DvqtpLTbqF8SPMCvqYAO_5g%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2022.%20The%20animal%20was%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20per%20the%20Department.%20Gamini%20is%20being%20housed%20in%20the%20enclosure%20for%20further%20health%20checks.%20Previously%2C%20cheetahs%20Pavan%2C%20Gaurav%2C%20and%20Shaurya%20were%20brought%20into%20enclosures%20on%20July%2014%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efollowed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Aasha%20and%20Dheera%20on%20July%2020.%20%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20male%20cheetah%20Pavak%20was%20also%20captured%20on%20July%2023%20and%20brought%20into%20an%20enclosure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Forest%20Department%20on%20July%2023%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fminforestmp%2Fstatus%2F1683168425772740610%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20currently%2C%2011%20cheetahs%20are%20housed%20in%20enclosures%2C%20or%20bomas%2C%20in%20the%20Park%3A%20six%20males%20and%20five%20females.%20It%20also%20quoted%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(Wildlife)%20Aseem%20Srivastava%20as%20saying%20that%20continuous%20monitoring%20of%20cheetahs%20is%20being%20done%20in%20Kuno.%20The%20tests%20are%20being%20conducted%20by%20the%20Kuno%20wildlife%20veterinary%20team%20and%20experts%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20another%20FD%20tweet%20on%20June%2023%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FD%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fminforestmp%2Fstatus%2F1683168428016771073%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20radio%20collars%20of%20six%20cheetahs%20have%20been%20removed%20following%20health%20tests%20so%20far.%20The%20currently%20collarless%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20which%20the%20government%20claims%20are%20%E2%80%9Chealthy%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20are%20Gaurav%2C%20Shaurya%2C%20Pavan%2C%20Pavak%2C%20Aasha%20and%20Dheera%2C%20per%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fradio-collars-of-6-cheetahs-at-knp-removed-for-health-examination-forest-officials%2F615441.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2024.%20An%20official%20claimed%20that%20while%20some%20individuals%20had%20small%20lesions%2C%20the%20brothers%20Gaurav%20and%20Shaurya%20%E2%80%93%20brought%20in%20from%20Namibia%20%E2%80%93%20had%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20infections%E2%80%9D%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fradio-collars-of-six-kuno-cheetahs-removed-two-had-severe-infection-8856470%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20same%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Difficult%20to%20catch%E2%80%99%