n%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20filed%20for%20divorce%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20killing%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%20Dadar%20area%20of%20the%20city%20in%20December%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trigger%20for%20the%20murder%20was%20the%20estranged%20couple's%20disagreement%20over%20the%20alimony%20amount%2C%20which%20Umesh%20was%20supposed%20to%20pay%20once%20the%20divorce%20was%20finalised%2C%20the%20prosecution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20sister%20in%20her%20deposition%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20there%20was%20a%20difference%20of%20opinion%20between%20the%20couple%20after%20six%20months%20of%20marriage%20and%20they%20would%20quarrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmesh%20had%20become%20suspicious%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20she%20would%20come%20home%20late%20from%20work.%20When%20Tanuja%20became%20pregnant%2C%20he%20started%20doubting%20her%20character%20and%20insisted%20on%20having%20a%20DNA%20test%20done%20and%20it%20proved%20his%20paternity%2C%20the%20witness%20told%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20also%20recorded%20the%20testimony%20of%20the%20accused's%20son%2C%20his%20neighbours%20and%20the%20investigating%20officer%20of%20the%20case%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690218420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fiof8givc_arrest-generic_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-dentist-sentenced-to-life-in-jail-for-killing-wife-in-front-of-son-4237092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sessions%20court%20here%20on%20Monday%20sentenced%20a%20city-based%20dentist%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20brutally%20killing%20his%20wife%20in%20front%20of%20their%20five-year-old%20son%20in%202016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%