802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20Greek%20village%20of%20Massari%2C%20on%20the%20east%20coast%20of%20Rhodes%2C%20they're%20clearing%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftourists-and-villagers-join-exodus-as-traumatic-wildfires-tear-across-rhodes-12926802%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-and-villagers-join-exodus-as-traumatic-wildfires-tear-across-rhodes-12926802%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-and-villagers-join-exodus-as-traumatic-wildfires-tear-across-rhodes-12926802%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rhodes%20wildfires%20are%20'like%20a%20biblical%20catastrophe'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690215561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FEDA8%2Fproduction%2F_130504806_beachumbrella-bbc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66294583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20tourists%20evacuate%2C%20the%20wildfires%20have%20come%20at%20great%20personal%20cost%20to%20the%20Greek%20island's%20residents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A348%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66294583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66294583.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66294583.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Uttam%20Kumar%2C%20The%20True%20Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttam%20Kumar%20blazed%20like%20a%20meteor%20and%20vanished%20like%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal's%20classiest%20filmstar%20was%20shrouded%20in%20mysteries.%20I%20never%20met%20him%20but%20heard%20countless%20stories%20about%20the%20person%20and%20his%20acting%20prowess.%20And%20his%20temperament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20book%20has%20hit%20the%20stands.%20It%20is%20on%20bars%20and%20the%20Kolkata%20Maidan%2C%20the%20huge%20green%20cover%20that%20is%20home%20to%20some%20iconic%20football%20clubs%2C%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20cricket%20stadium%2C%20and%20the%20majestic%20Victoria%20Memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20talks%20about%20various%20places%20in%20Maidan%20where%20top%20writers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20thinkers%20would%20go%20to%20drink%2C%20some%20even%20carrying%20small%20bottles%20of%20whisky%20in%20their%20pockets.%20The%20author%2C%20Rahul%20Purakayastha%2C%20refers%20to%20Bimal%20Deb's%20poem%2C%20%3Cem%3EUttamkumarer%3C%2Fem%3E%20morning%20walk%20which%20translates%20into%20Uttam%20Kumar's%20morning%20walk%2C%20and%20writes%20that%20the%20actor%20saw%20Calcutta%20policemen%20shooting%20three%20people%20at%20point-blank%20range%20in%20the%20maidan.%20Those%20killed%20-%20it%20was%20nothing%20but%20an%20act%20that%20later%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20encounter%20killing%20-%20were%20Naxalites.%20Among%20those%20shot%20dead%20was%20seasoned%20Naxalite%20leader%20Saroj%20Dutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttam%20Kumar%2C%20probably%20threatened%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20Police%20brass%2C%20quietly%20left%20Calcutta%20and%20shifted%20to%20Mumbai.%20Apparently%2C%20Uttam%20had%20narrated%20the%20incident%20to%20some%20of%20his%20confidants%20who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20alerted%20the%20cops.%20Once%20the%20dust%20settled%20down%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20Calcutta%20and%20started%20shooting%20for%20a%20host%20of%20films%20he%20had%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20you%20will%20not%20find%20a%20single%20person%20in%20Kolkata%20who%20will%20say%20the%20star%20was%20a%20coward%20and%20did%20not%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20early%20morning%20killings%20in%20Maidan%20with%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttam%20Kumar%20was%20the%20darling%20of%20the%20masses%20in%20Bengal%2C%20who%20had%20christened%20him%20Mahanayak%20-%20superstar.%20No%20male%20actor%20in%20Bengal%20could%20reach%20the%20status%20Uttam%20Kumar%20had%20reached%20in%20a%20span%20of%20three%20decades.%20He%20acted%20in%20over%20200%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20man%20of%20varying%20moods.%20He%20once%20got%20up%20from%20the%20dining%20table%20and%20started%20walking%20in%20the%20main%20road%20because%20his%20second%20wife%2C%20Supriya%20Chowdhury%2C%20did%20not%20prepare%20a%20particular%20dish%20the%20star%20had%20requested.%20Crowds%20started%20gathering%20in%20hundreds%2C%20then%20thousands%2C%20seeing%20their%20top%20star%20walking%20in%20the%20streets%20all%20by%20himself.%20A%20distraught%20Supriya%20started%20following%20her%20husband%2C%20she%20forgot%20to%20wear%20her%20shoes.%20Soon%2C%20the%20tar-laced%20hot%20streets%20of%20Calcutta%20were%20making%20things%20difficult%20for%20her.%20Supriya%2C%20reportedly%2C%20was%20weeping%20profusely%20and%20asking%20her%20husband%20to%20pardon%20her%20for%20the%20lapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20cops%20from%20the%20Park%20Street%20police%20station%20rushed%20to%20the%20scene%20and%20senior%20officers%20told%20Uttam%20Kumar%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20get%20into%20the%20police%20jeep%2C%20or%20else%20there%20could%20be%20a%20major%20stampede.%20It%20is%20rumoured%20that%20Uttam%20Kumar%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20his%20wife%20for%20over%20a%20week%20after%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20countless%20stories%20revolving%20around%20this%20handsome%20star.%20I%20heard%20from%20some%20senior%20actors%20in%20Kolkata%20how%20Uttam%20Kumar%20would%20not%20get%20a%20bypass%20surgery%20done%20to%20control%20his%20heart%20ailments.%20He%20told%20his%20friends%20how%20can%20a%20doctor%20cut%20up%20the%20chest%20of%20a%20star%2C%20and%20take%20a%20look%20at%20his%20heart.%20Won't%20the%20star%20look%20horrible%20after%20the%20operation%2C%20asked%20Uttam%20Kumar.%20The%20doctors%20felt%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20researching%20for%20a%20book%20on%20Uttam%20Kumar%20and%20have%20been%20told%20some%20interesting%20stories%20about%20the%20actor.%20One%20revolved%20around%20his%20failed%20attempt%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20Bollywood%20with%20Choti%20Si%20Mulaqat%20featuring%20Vaijayantimala%20Bali.%20The%20movie%20was%20released%20in%20a%20few%20theatres%20in%20Bombay%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20India.%20There%20were%20rumours%20that%20the%20all-powerful%20Kapoor%20family%20messed%20up%20the%20show%2C%20ostensibly%20because%20Uttam%20Kumar%20had%20refused%20a%20role%20Raj%20Kapoor%20had%20offered%20him%20in%20Sangam.%20The%20role%2C%20eventually%2C%20went%20to%20Rajendra%20Kumar%20but%20Raj%20Kapoor%20remembered%20the%20rejection.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20rejection%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20had%20rejected%20an%20earlier%20offer%20to%20act%20in%20the%20lead%20role%20of%20%3Cem%3EJagte%20Raho%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20could%20never%20make%20any%20mark%20in%20Bombay%20(now%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20strange%20how%20Uttam%20Kumar%20failed%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20stars%20like%20Shashi%20Kapoor%2C%20Dharmendra%20and%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20were%20big%20fans%20of%20Uttam%20Kumar's%20style%20of%20acting.%20I%20read%20somewhere%20Uttam%20Kumar%20was%20also%20included%20in%20the%20cast%20of%20Ajnabi%20which%20was%20directed%20by%20Shakti%20Samanta.%20But%20when%20the%20movie%20eventually%20hit%20the%20theatres%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20was%20not%20among%20the%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20misadventure%20messed%20up%20Uttam%20Kumar.%20The%20actor%20faced%20huge%20financial%20losses%20and%20had%20to%20sell%20off%20some%20of%20his%20properties%20to%20clear%20the%20dues.%20And%20it%20was%20then%20he%20suffered%20his%20first%20heart%20attack.%20What%20was%20worse%2C%20those%20who%20messed%20up%20his%20life%20in%20Bombay%20were%20none%20other%20than%20his%20Bengali%20friends%20from%20Calcutta.%20A%20month%20after%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%2C%20during%20a%20shoot%2C%20told%20his%20cameramen%20friends%20to%20shoot%20him%20behind%20a%20large%2C%20artificial%20spider%20web.%20After%20the%20shoot%20was%20over%20and%20the%20prints%20hit%20the%20newspapers%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20told%20Supriya%20that%20this%20was%20his%20life's%20story.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20wants%20to%20put%20a%20web%20around%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Supriya.%20He%20was%20also%20upset%20because%20Soumitra%20Chatterjee%2C%20his%20junior%20and%20a%20rival%2C%20often%20told%20people%20that%20the%20top%20Bengali%20actress%20should%20have%20been%20paired%20with%20him%20and%20not%20with%20Uttam%20Kumar.%20But%20directors%20thought%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20met%20with%20Supriya%20a%20year%20before%20she%20died.%20She%20sat%20down%20and%20narrated%20some%20wonderful%20stories%20about%20her%20life%20and%20times%20with%20the%20legendary%20superstar.%20Those%20were%20the%20black-and-white%20trailblazer%20days%20of%20Bengali%20cinema%2C%20there%20was%20no%20WhatsApp%2C%20no%20Insta%2C%20yet%20his%20movies%20did%20brilliantly%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20laughed%20when%20she%20said%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20for%20her%20to%20keep%20Uttam%20Kumar%20away%20from%20women%20who%20would%20crowd%20his%20shooting%20studios.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20funny%20was%20that%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20marry%20him%20almost%20instantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20was%20under%20severe%20medication%20while%20she%20spoke%20to%20us.%20Every%20five%20minutes%20she%20would%20take%20a%20break%2C%20drink%20some%20water%2C%20and%20say%20she%20normally%20doesn't%20give%20interviews%20without%20cash.%20She%20was%20doing%20it%20only%20because%20it%20was%20all%20about%20Uttam%20Kumar.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20much%20I%20should%20have%20paid%20her.%20I%20realised%20I%20had%20not%20carried%20the%20customary%20sweets%20during%20my%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20veteran%20actress%20poured%20her%20heart%20out.%20She%20narrated%20some%2025%20small%20stories%20that%20I%20plan%20to%20carry%20in%20my%20book%20before%20each%20chapter.%20One%20revolved%20around%20Uttam%20Kumar's%20worshipping%20of%20Lakshmi%2C%20the%20Indian%20goddess%20of%20wealth%2C%20with%20loads%20of%20fanfare%20at%20his%20home.%20He%20-%20claimed%20Supriya%20-%20had%20a%20vision%20of%20the%20goddess%20on%20his%20terrace.%20And%20then%2C%20the%20superstar%20was%20encouraged%20to%20see%20a%20white%20owl%20that%20visited%20his%20home%20every%20evening%20for%20a%20week%20before%20the%20puja.%20The%20white%20owl%20is%20considered%20auspicious%20in%20India%20because%20it%20is%20the%20carrier%20of%20the%20goddess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20interestingly%2C%20was%20how%20Uttam%20Kumar%20never%20wanted%20her%20to%20wear%20a%20nightgown%20in%20bed.%20He%20insisted%20she%20wear%20a%20saree%2C%20not%20necessarily%20a%20new%20one%2C%20before%20hitting%20the%20bed.%20I%20thought%20it%20a%20little%20bizarre%3B%20how%20can%20you%20handle%20a%20saree%20in%20bed%3F%20But%20then%2C%20that's%20what%20stars%20are%20made%20of.%20Their%20style%2C%20whims%2C%20and%20fancies%20are%20totally%20different%20from%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttam%20Kumar%2C%20said%20Supriya%2C%20was%20indeed%20handsome.%20His%20title%20role%20in%20Satyajit%20Ray'sNayak%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20The%20Star%2C%20was%20one%20of%20his%20finest.%20I%20was%20told%20Elizabeth%20Taylor%20was%20impressed%20seeing%20him%20on%20screen%20and%20wanted%20to%20meet%20him.%20It%20never%20happened.%20Worse%2C%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20Soumitra%20Chatterjee%20-%20a%20favourite%20of%20Ray%20-%20asked%20his%20friends%20how%20Ray%20could%20pick%20Uttam%20Kumar%20and%20not%20him%20for%20the%20movie.%20He%20probably%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20ask%20Ray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legendary%20director%20has%20himself%20recounted%20the%20premiere%20of%20Nayak%20and%20how%20Uttam%20looked%20super%20smart%20in%20a%20new%20suit%20and%20Supriya%20looked%20ravishing%20in%20a%20beautiful%20saree.%20Expectedly%2C%20the%20crowds%20went%20berserk%20after%20the%20movie%2C%20and%20Ray%20lost%20control.%20The%20fans%20tore%20off%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20star's%20suit%20and%20the%20cops%20had%20to%20rescue%20him%20and%20take%20him%20to%20Oberoi%20Grand.%20Ray%20said%20in%20one%20of%20his%20interviews%20that%20he%20finally%20realised%20why%20Uttam%20was%20considered%20the%20biggest%20star%20of%20Bengal%2C%20the%20first%20one%20to%20get%20a%20national%20award%20after%20it%20was%20instituted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20pity%20he%20died%20so%20young%3B%20he%20was%20in%20his%20early%20fifties.%20Liquor%20and%20an%20erratic%20lifestyle%20had%20messed%20up%20his%20life%2C%20he%20was%20no%20longer%20handsome.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20realised%20his%20time%20was%20almost%20up%2C%20he%20suffered%20a%20severe%20heart%20attack%20on%20the%20sets%20of%20Ogo%20Bodhu%20Sundori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20incidents%20that%20happened%20just%20before%20he%20died%20will%20stay%20with%20me%20forever.%20One%2C%20his%20favourite%20makeup%20room%20was%20offered%20to%20a%20top%20Bollywood%20star%2C%20and%20Uttam%20Kumar%20was%20made%20to%20wait.%20He%20didn't%20like%20it%20at%20all%20and%20said%20if%20there%20is%20a%20door%20to%20enter%20life%2C%20there%20is%20a%20door%20to%20exit.%20And%20that%20he%20knew%20the%20exit.%20The%20second%20one%20revolved%20around%20Punu%20Sen%2C%20who%20worked%20very%20closely%20with%20Ray.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20had%20asked%20Sen%20if%20Ray%20had%20some%20roles%20for%20him%20and%20that%20he%20didn't%20like%20the%20roles%20offered%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20his%20conversation%20with%20Sen%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20breathed%20his%20last%20amidst%20some%20serious%20rumours%20that%20a%20lifesaving%20drug%20was%20not%20offered%20to%20him%20when%20he%20was%20hovering%20between%20life%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%20No%20one%20has%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Supriya%20told%20me%20before%20winding%20up%20the%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BRemember%20one%20thing%2C%20someone%20who%20is%20stretched%20between%20multiple%20women%20can%20never%20live%20a%20peaceful%20life.%20He%20will%20always%20be%20tormented.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20should%20know%2C%20she%20was%20a%20big%20slice%20in%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20Bengal's%20biggest%20movie%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShantanu%20Guha%20Ray's%20book%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%3A%20The%20Star%2C%20will%20hit%20the%20stands%20in%20March%202024.%20It%20will%20have%2025%20exclusive%20stories%20about%20the%20star%2C%20narrated%20by%20Supriya%20Chowdhury.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690215420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqbu0to7o_uttam-kumar_625x300_24_July_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Futtam-kumar-the-true-star-4237811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal's%20classiest%20filmstar%20was%20shrouded%20in%20mysteries.%20I%20never%20met%20him%20but%20heard%20countless%20stories%20about%20the%20person%20and%20his%20acting%20prowess.%20And%20his%20temperament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A103%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Futtam-kumar-the-true-star-4237811%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Futtam-kumar-the-true-star-4237811%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Futtam-kumar-the-true-star-4237811%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Protests%2C%20Israeli%20Parliament%20Approves%20Contentious%20Judicial%20Reform%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24213937%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-24T213901.301.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20lawmakers%20on%20Monday%20approved%20a%20key%20portion%20of%20Prime%