ng%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20opposition%20parties%20continued%20to%20demand%20a%20statement%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20parliament%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20hold%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%20and%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20not%20wanting%20a%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20even%20as%20the%20opposition%20has%20remained%20firm%20on%20its%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20by%20Modi%20inside%20the%20House%20and%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Rules%20of%20Procedures%20and%20Conduct%20of%20Business%E2%80%99.%20The%20government%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20only%20agreed%20to%20a%20short-term%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20127.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20got%20off%20to%20a%20stormy%20start%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20parliament%20with%20protests%20and%20counter-protests%20staged%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20statue%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20repeated%20adjournments%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20invited%20the%20home%20minister%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20Manipur%20on%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20and%20a%20discussion%20has%20been%20demanded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20ready%20for%20a%20discussion.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20the%20opposition%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20a%20discussion.%20I%20urge%20the%20opposition%20to%20allow%20a%20discussion.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20the%20country%20to%20have%20a%20discussion%20on%20this%20sensitive%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Sunday%2C%20July%2023%2C%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20also%20appealed%20with%20%E2%80%9Cfolded%20hands%E2%80%9D%20to%20opposition%20parties%20to%20join%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wish%20that%20there%20should%20be%20a%20good%20discussion%20on%20this%20in%20the%20House%2C%20where%20all%20political%20parties%20will%20participate.%20Nobody%20should%20run%20away%20from%20the%20debate.%20It%20is%20my%20request%20to%20the%20opposition%20with%20folded%20hands%2C%20do%20not%20run%20away%20from%20the%20discussion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20however%2C%20has%20demanded%20a%20debate%20under%20Rule%20267.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20debate%20in%20the%20House%20under%20Rule%20267.%20But%20the%20ministers%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20say%20that%20there%20will%20be%20only%20short%20duration%20discussion%2C%20another%20one%20says%20that%20there%20will%20be%20only%20half%20an%20hour%20discussion.%20Rule%20267%20debate%20can%20go%20on%20for%20hours%2C%20voting%20can%20also%20happen%2C%20we%20want%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Congress%20chief%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20outside%20parliament%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14154208%2F09mallikarjun-kharge-in-rs.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14154208%2F09mallikarjun-kharge-in-rs.jpeg%20670w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14154208%2F09mallikarjun-kharge-in-rs-300x149.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640483%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22332%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20that.%20Somebody%20says%20half%20an%20hour%20discussion%2C%20another%20says%20short%20duration%20discussion.%20The%20problem%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20solved%20with%20your%20discussion.%20You%20are%20representative%20of%20140%20crore%20people.%20Why%20are%20you%20not%20coming%20to%20the%20House%20and%20telling%20the%20truth%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERule%20267%20under%20which%20the%20opposition%20wants%20a%20discussion%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CAny%20member%2C%20may%2C%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20Chairman%2C%20move%20that%20any%20rule%20may%20be%20suspended%20in%20its%20application%20to%20a%20motion%20related%20to%20the%20business%20listed%20before%20the%20Council%20of%20that%20day%20and%20if%20the%20motion%20is%20carried%2C%20the%20rule%20in%20question%20shall%20be%20suspended%20for%20the%20time%20being%3A%20Provided%20further%20that%20this%20rule%20shall%20not%20apply%20where%20specific%20provision%20already%20exists%20for%20suspension%20of%20a%20rule%20under%20a%20particular%20chapter%20of%20the%20Rules.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20does%20not%20want%20to%20move%20ahead%20with%20Rule%20267%20and%20wants%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20176.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20rule%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CAny%20member%20desirous%20of%20raising%20discussion%20on%20a%20matter%20of%20urgent%20public%20importance%20may%20give%20notice%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20Secretary-General%20specifying%20clearly%20and%20precisely%20the%20matter%20to%20be%20raised%3A%20Provided%20that%20the%20notice%20shall%20be%20accompanied%20by%20an%20explanatory%20note%20stating%20reasons%20for%20raising%20discussion%20on%20the%20matter%20in%20question%3A%20Provided%20further%20that%20the%20notice%20shall%20be%20supported%20by%20the%20signatures%20of%20at%20least%20two%20other%20members.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203%2C%20in%20which%20over%20150%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20left%20tens%20of%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20statement%20by%20Modi%20inside%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3Ebroke%20his%20silence%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20and%20spoke%20outside%20the%20parliament%20building%20on%20Thursday%2C%20he%20specifically%20referred%20to%20the%20harrowing%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20the%20day%20before%20%E2%80%93%20showing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Etwo%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kangpokpi%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20and%20collapse%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20also%20mentioned%20the%20Congress-ruled%20states%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20and%20asked%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20act%20against%20violence%20against%20women.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20saw%20repeated%20adjournments%20as%20the%20opposition%20continued%20to%20raise%20slogans%20condemning%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20and%20demanding%20that%20he%20address%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Singh%20was%20suspended%20by%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20for%20%E2%80%9Crepeatedly%20violating%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20Chair%E2%80%9D%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20protested%20in%20parliament%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20