n.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20radium%20strip%20cautionary%20blockades%20either.%20What%20you%20are%20seeing%20is%20an%20improved%20condition.%20You%20can%20imagine%20how%20it%20must%20have%20been%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20homeopathy%20practitioner%20Mahendra%20said.%20After%20a%20point%2C%20the%20correspondents%20had%20to%20get%20off%20their%20motorcycle%20and%20travel%20on%20foot%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2013%2C%20a%20Kanwar%20Yatri%20named%20Rajaram%20Chauhan%20died%20on%20the%20under%20construction%20Bhaktipath%20Road%20after%20falling%20into%20a%20water-filled%20pit%2C%20which%20had%20an%20exposed%20electrical%20wire.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20on%20fixing%20the%20faults%20in%20the%20safety%20measures%20of%20the%20construction%2C%20and%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Kanvariya%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20ADM%20Amit%20Singh%20said%20responding%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20neglect%20by%20authorities.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20places%20where%20officials%20have%20not%20adopted%20standard%20safety%20measures%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20acted%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20speech%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20said%20that%20commuters%20will%20temporarily%20face%20problems%20but%20that%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20the%20roads%20of%20Ayodhya%20will%20look%20like%20the%20Rajpath%20in%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20have%20named%20it%20Rampath%20after%20Lord%20Ram.%20Earlier%20Ayodhya%20did%20not%20have%20such%20broad%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasised.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%20Jitin%20Prasada%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20public%20works%20department%20minister%2C%20had%20asked%20officials%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20work%20on%20the%20arterial%20road.%20And%20in%20March%202023%2C%20district%20magistrate%20Nitish%