20picks%20up%20pace%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20opened%20in%20January%202024%2C%20Ayodhya%20Ji%20is%20also%20bracing%20for%20a%20major%20transformation%2C%20with%20the%20new%20Ayodhya%20Ji%20bearing%20little%20or%20no%20resemblance%20with%20the%20old%20city%20that%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEkFnsU6A07%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEkFnsU6A07%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Government%20of%20UP%20(%40UPGovt)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUPGovt%2Fstatus%2F1679341928515776514%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20tweet%2C%20purporting%20to%20endorse%20the%20line%20that%20the%20city%20will%20have%20%E2%80%9Clittle%20or%20no%20resemblance%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20city%20of%20the%20Vedas%2C%20Adityanath%20has%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CTreta%20Yuga%E2%80%9D%20will%20come%20back%20with%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20new%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Raghuvansh%20Mani%20Tripathi%2C%20quoted%20earlier%20in%20the%20piece%2C%20said%20that%20meetings%20with%20members%20of%20parliament%20and%20legislative%20assembly%20have%20not%20yielded%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Lallu%20Singh%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Ayodhya%20for%20a%20comment%20but%20he%20was%20unavailable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20need%20for%20the%20Rampath%20as%20there%20is%20already%20a%20four-lane%20road%20that%20connects%20with%20Ayodhya.%20Due%20to%20the%20Rampath%20project%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20houses%20and%20shops%20have%20been%20demolished.%20Most%20of%20these%20lands%20are%20Nazul%20lands.%20So%20the%20government%20is%20not%20compensating%20for%20the%20land%20but%20only%20for%20the%20buildings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tripathi%20said%2C%20adding%20how%20business%20owners%20will%20have%20to%20spend%20much%20more%20to%20relocate%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20bought%20the%20house%20in%201971%20through%20mutation%20of%20property%20and%20other%20necessary%20documentation.%20I%20received%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20for%20the%20partial%20demolition.%20I%20lost%20two%20out%20of%20four%20rooms%20in%20this%20process.%20Now%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20my%20family%20to%20adjust%20in%20this%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tripathi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESP%20trade%20unionist%20Nandu%20Gupta%20fears%20that%20in%20order%20to%20enhance%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20the%20newly%20constructed%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20the%20administration%20will%20also%20clear%20the%20street%20vendors%20and%20small%20%3Cem%3Ethela%3C%2Fem%3E%20owners%20who%20have%20been%20earning%20their%20livelihoods%20on%20the%20roadside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20comrades%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20deity%20Ram%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20protect%20his%20Ayodhya%20and%20its%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690198219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162930%2FIMG_2541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fayodhya-rampath-demolition-construction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20rampant%20construction%20and%20demolition%20efforts%2C%20at%20risk%20are%20people%E2%80%99s%20houses%2C%20businesses%20and%20a%20275-year-old%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fayodhya-rampath-demolition-construction%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sex%20Ratio%20Falls%20in%20Several%20States%20Despite%20NITI%20Aayog%20Success%20Report%20on%20'Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2Fhandpump.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20sex%20ratio%20in%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20states%2C%20including%20Karnataka%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Haryana%2C%20saw%20a%20decline%20between%202021-22%20and%202022-23%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20occurred%20despite%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1695199%5C%22%3Esuccess%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%20by%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20which%20uses%20sex%20ratio%20at%20birth%20as%20a%20parameter%20for%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fover-dozen-states-saw-decline-in-sex-ratio-since-2020-govt-1240024.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ladakh%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20only%20state%2FUnion%20territory%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20number%20of%20girl%20children%20is%20more%20than%20boys.%20It%20has%20a%20sex%20ratio%20of%201%2C023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Assam%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20has%20shown%20an%20improvement%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20fell%20from%20949%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20940%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20slight%20recovery%20in%202022%E2%80%9323%20when%20it%20marginally%20rose%20to%20945.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20was%20927%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%2C%20fell%20to%20924%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20further%20fell%20to%20916%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%20The%20sex%20ratio%20in%20West%20Bengal%20fell%20from%20949%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20943%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%20and%20then%20to%20932%20in%202022%E2%80%9323%2C%20said%20the%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20saw%20a%20decline%20from%20917%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20915%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20then%20fell%20to%20895%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%20Chandigarh%2C%20too%2C%20registered%20a%20steep%20fall.%20It%20first%20rose%20from%20935%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20941%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20then%20down%20to%20902%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Himachal%2C%20it%20fell%20from%20944%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20941%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%20and%20932%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%20and%20Kerala%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20showed%20improvement.%20In%20UP%2C%20it%20first%20fell%20from%20940%20in%202020-21%20to%20939%20in%202021-22%20but%20then%20improved%20to%20944%20in%202022-23.%20In%20Assam%2C%20it%20rose%20from%20942%20in%202020-21%20to%20944%20in%202021-22%2C%20and%20then%20further%20rose%20to%20951%20in%202022-23.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20(946)%20remained%20the%20same%20in%20all%20three%20years%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20further%20said%20that%20several%20states%20had%20significant%20amounts%20of%20unutilised%20funds%20that%20were%20allocated%20for%20the%20scheme%20by%20the%20WCD%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%2C%20Haryana%20utilised%20only%20Rs%20142.26%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%20249.83%20lakh%2C%20and%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20it%20used%20only%20Rs%2027.09%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%20162.8%20lakh%20it%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20utilised%20Rs%20742.60%20lakh%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20even%20when%20Rs%20577.95%20lakh%20was%20released%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20but%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20it%20used%20only%20Rs%20162.89%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%201%2C499.45%20lakh%20that%20was%20allocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20effective%20implementation%20and%20management%20of%20the%20allocated%20resources%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690197620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2Fhandpump.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsex-ratio-falls-in-several-states-despite-niti-aayog-success-report-on-beti-bachao-beti-padhao%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ladakh%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20only%20state%2FUnion%20territory%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20number%20of%20girl%20children%20is%20more%20than%20boys%2C%20with%20a%20sex%20ratio%20of%201%2C023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsex-ratio-falls-in-several-states-despite-niti-aayog-success-report-on-beti-bachao-beti-padhao%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20George%20Alagiah's%20extraordinary%20career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690197053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5F4F%2Fproduction%2F_130499342_p0g2m6pn.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-66200509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22George%20Alagiah%2C%20one%20of%20the%20BBC's%20longest-serving%20and%20most%20respected%20journalists%2C%20has%20died%20at%2067.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A664%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fuk-66200509%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Russia%20attacks%20grain%20stores%20at%20River%20Danube%20ports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A16901967150