n-food-recipes-pakora-map-of-india-cuisine-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epakoras%20%3C%2Fem%3E(fritters)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20says%20are%20his%20favourite!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20hunt%20for%20restaurants%20to%20enjoy%20his%20favourite%20Indian%20dishes%20any%20more.%20On%20his%20recent%20tour%20to%20India%2C%20Daniel%20learnt%20to%20cook%20various%20kinds%20of%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Epakora%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealu%20gobi%2C%20pulao%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20many%20other%20delicacies%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20foodies.%20Every%20time%20we%20visit%20a%20new%20country%2C%20we%20try%20to%20learn%20about%20its%20cuisine.%20When%20we%20came%20to%20India%2C%20we%20found%20the%20flavours%20of%20the%20food%20to%20be%20completely%20different%20from%20the%20Indian%20food%20we%20had%20in%20Spain.%20Here%20the%20spices%20have%20a%20stronger%20flavour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1689859178.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Cuenca%20and%20his%20wife%20Maria%20Naharro%20learning%20to%20cook%20Indian%20delicacies%20from%20Shashi.%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1689859178.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1689859178-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1689859178-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1689859178-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20ht