%20to%20try.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20keep%20practising%20and%20moving%20between%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F245585%2Fat-21-he-started-selling-momos-from-his-home-kitchen-now-has-rs-180-cr-turnover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20my%20home%20kitchen%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20my%20aunt%E2%80%99s%20kitchen.%20There%20have%20been%20errors%20too%2C%20but%20with%20time%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20right%20balance.%20Initially%2C%20I%20was%20funding%20it%20myself%20with%20the%20money%20I%20earned%20from%20a%20part-time%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20were%20not%20really%20aware%20of%20the%20plan%20I%20had%20and%20they%20probably%20looked%20at%20it%20as%20a%20hobby.%20When%20I%20received%20good%20reviews%20from%20my%20parents%20and%20friends%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20a%20business%20plan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20earlier%20during%20Diwali%2C%20Digvijay%E2%80%99s%20father%20had%20purchased%20a%20car%20for%20which%20he%20received%20a%20box%20of%20chocolates%20as%20a%20present.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20day%20I%20asked%20the%20showroom%20manager%20how%20many%20cars%20were%20sold%2C%20and%20he%20said%20more%20than%2060.%20They%20all%20were%20given%20boxes%20of%20chocolate.%20This%20gave%20me%20the%20idea%20of%20contacting%20hotel%20owners%20and%20car%20showroom%20owners%20to%20sell%20my%20chocolates%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20a%20small%20team%20of%208%20people%2C%20Digvijay%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20introduce%20coming%20generations%20to%20indigenously%20grown%20fruits.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1689164331-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323573%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20small%20team%20of%208%20people%2C%20Digvijay%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20introduce%20coming%20generations%20to%20indigenously%20grown%20fruits.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Digvijay%20Singh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Digvijay%20got%20his%20first%20order%20of%201%2C000%20chocolates%20from%20a%20car%20showroom%20owner.%20He%20also%20launched%20his%20brand%20under%20the%20name%20Saraam%20the%20same%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20happy%20beyond%20words%20and%20was%20very%20excited%20for%20the%20future%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20to%20kill%20time%20has%20today%20become%20a%20successful%20chocolate%20brand%20that%20has%20made%20a%20lifetime%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20sold%20over%202%20tonnes%20of%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20Indian%20fruits%20to%20the%20limelight%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Digvijay%20came%20across%20an%20article%20online%20on%20how%20there%20were%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20indigenous%20fruits%20that%20were%20being%20extinct.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20mentions%20of%20fruits%20that%20I%20have%20never%20even%20heard%20about%20and%20I%20was%20very%20shocked.%20For%20us%